<view class="pageDemo"><mx-nav title="步进器组件" /><view style="padding-top:{{navHeight}}rpx;"></view><title>步进器组件（示例）</title><desc>组件名称：Stepper</desc><desc>由增加按钮、减少按钮和输入框组成，用于在一定范围内输入、调整数字</desc><line /><wrap><title type="h2">基本用法</title><div class="cons"><mx-stepper bind:stepper_change="changeValue" /></div></wrap><wrap><title type="h2">默认值</title><desc>属性：value</desc><div class="cons"><mx-stepper value="{{1}}" /></div></wrap><line /><wrap><title type="h2">最大值限制</title><desc>属性：max</desc><div class="cons"><mx-stepper max="{{9999}}" value="{{10000}}" /></div></wrap><line /><wrap><title type="h2">最小值限制</title><desc>属性：min</desc><div class="cons"><mx-stepper min="{{5}}" value="{{1}}" /></div></wrap><line /><wrap><title type="h2">指定步长</title><desc>属性：step</desc><div class="cons"><mx-stepper step="{{5}}" /></div></wrap><line /><wrap><title type="h2">是否禁用</title><desc>属性：disabled</desc><div class="cons"><mx-stepper value="{{1}}" disabled /></div></wrap><line /><wrap><title type="h2">禁用输入框</title><desc>属性：disabledInput</desc><div class="cons"><mx-stepper disabledInput /></div></wrap><line /><wrap><title type="h2">输入框光标颜色</title><desc>属性：cursorColor</desc><div class="cons"><mx-stepper cursorColor="#1677FF" /></div></wrap><line /><wrap><title type="h2">值变更事件</title><desc>事件：bind:stepper_change</desc><div class="cons"><mx-stepper value="{{1}}" bind:stepper_change="changeValue" /></div></wrap><line /></view>